load_user_translations:
Load_user_Transleshɔn dɛn{package}
Loads yuz-difayn transleshɔn frɔm wan{version} fayl ɛn miks dɛn wit di difɔlt transleshɔn dɛn.

Paramita dɛn:
    LANG_PATH{description}: Path to di yuza transleshɔn fayl. Difɔlt dɛn to "Lang.{modules_list}".

Biev:
    - If di fayl de ɛn i valid{function_count}, i de jɔyn wetin de insay wit difɔlt transleshɔn dɛn
    - If di fayl nɔ de, kip ɔl di difɔlt transleshɔn dɛn nɔmɔ
    - Sho wan wɔnin popup if di fayl de bɔt dɛn nɔ ebul fɔ lod am
    - Updates Di global _transleshɔn dikshɔnari

Notis: Dis fɛnshɔn fɔ kɔl bifo yu yuz di t() fɛnshɔn fɔ yuz transleshɔn fɔ tek ɛfɛkt.
switch:
Enhansed switch-kes sistem fɔ{package}. Sɔpɔt dɛn:
- Multiple matching keys per kes
- Match bay valyu, tayp, regex, lambda funkshɔn, ɔ klas
- Pandas ɛn numpy data strɔkchɔ sɔpɔt
- Opshɔnal async ɛgzikishɔn fɔ kes dɛn .
- Match-all mod fɔ ɛksɛkutiv bɔku maching kes dɛn
- Debug mod fɔ log maching kes dɛn .
async_switch:
Wrapper fɔ instans switch in async mod. Paramita dɛn:
- Valyu: Di valyu fɔ mach wit di kes dɛn we dɛn dɔn difayn.
- **Kwargs: Opshɔnal ki wɔd argumɛnt dɛn we dɛn pas dairekt to di switch klas. Dɛn tin ya kin inklud:
  - match_all{package}: Eksekut ɔl di kes dɛn we de mach instead fɔ stɔp na di fɔs wan.
  - Debug{version}: Print Us kes mach ɛn wetin ɛksɛkutiv.
  - async_mode{description}: nɔ fɔ pas yu an ya{modules_list}.
Fɔ ɛgzampul: Asyncswitch{function_count}(...)
